{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<mfrac>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>MathML の <code>&lt;mfrac&gt;</code> 要素は分数を表示するのに使います。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">&lt;mfrac&gt;<em>numerator</em> <em>denominator</em>&lt;/mfrac&gt;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"attr-bevelled\"><code>bevelled</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>分数を表示する方法を指定します。<code>true</code> のとき分数線は斜線になります。つまりこの場合、分子・分母がスラッシュ (/) を挟んで左右に並ぶことになります。既定値の <code>false</code> の場合、分子は分母の上に載ります。<br>\n この属性は、非推奨で将来削除される予定です。代わりに U+2044 (fraction slash) を使用してください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-class-id-style\"><code>class</code>, <code>id</code>, <code>style</code></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS\">スタイルシート</a> で装飾を行なう際に使われます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-denomalign\"><code>denomalign</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>分数の下に分母をどう揃えるかを指定します。取り得る値は <code>left</code>、<code>center</code> (既定値) と <code>right</code> です。<br>\n この属性は、非推奨で近日中に廃止されます。代わりに CSS を用いて <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/text-align\">text-align</a></code> を指定してください。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-href\"><code>href</code></dt>\n <dd>特定の URI へのハイパーリンクを設定するのに使われます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-linethickness\"><code>linethickness</code></dt>\n <dd>分数の水平線の太さ。既定値は <code>medium</code> で、<code>thin</code>、<code>thick</code> や、それ以外の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Length\">length 値</a> が取り得ます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathbackground\"><code>mathbackground</code></dt>\n <dd>数式の背景色を指定するために使われます。<code>#rgb</code>、<code>#rrggbb</code>のような16進表現のほか、HTMLで定められた<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">色キーワード</a>を使用できます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathcolor\"><code>mathcolor</code></dt>\n <dd>数式自体 (テキストと分数線) の色を設定するために使われます。<code>#rgb</code>、<code>#rrggbb</code> のような 16 進表現のほか、HTMLで定められた<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\">色キーワード</a>を使用できます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-numalign\"><code>numalign</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>分数の上に分子をどう揃えるかを指定します。取り得る値は <code>left</code>、<code>center</code> (既定値) と <code>right</code> です。<br>\n この属性は、非推奨で将来削除される予定です。代わりに CSS の <code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/text-align\">text-align</a></code> を使用してください。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>レンダリングのサンプル (画像): <img alt=\"(a/b)/(c/d)\" src=\"/files/3194/mfrac.png\" style=\"margin-left: 10px; vertical-align: middle;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>ブラウザーのレンダリング結果: <math> <mfrac bevelled=\"true\"> <mfrac> <mi> a </mi> <mi> b </mi> </mfrac> <mfrac> <mi> c </mi> <mi> d </mi> </mfrac> </mfrac> </math></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mfrac</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">bevelled</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mfrac</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> a <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> b <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mfrac</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mfrac</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> c <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> d <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mfrac</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mfrac</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ステータス</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.mfrac\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">mfrac の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>現在の仕様</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.mfrac\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">mfrac の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>初回の仕様</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.mfrac","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"属性","id":"attributes"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"MathML の <mfrac> 要素は分数を表示するのに使います。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<mfrac>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<mfrac>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"mfrac","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mathml/element/mfrac","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/mathml/element/mfrac/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML 要素リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac","title":"<mfrac>"}],"pageTitle":"<mfrac> - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}